A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, and a robotics startup attracts attention by flying a small drone above its booth. Tech companies display demo screens showcasing their latest apps, and healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos. Volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures. Small groups analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic as students exit, carrying tote bags and a stack of business cards.
